'''R2-X3''' was an [[R2-series astromech droid/Legends|R2-series astromech droid]] which was once found on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. He was bought there by a [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] for 500 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] and was taken on his [[YT-1300 light freighter/Legends|YT-1300]] [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] to several other planets.

